snippet.title: Let's Play Aidyn Chronicles: The First Mage - Episode 1
snippet.description:
For my first ever let's play, I decided to start a new playthrough of Aidyn Chronicles: the first Mage, a game for the Nintendo 64.

Plz note that if you never played this game before, my let's play videos WILL contain a large amount of spoilers.
I Hope you enjoy watching them as much as I enjoy making them.

Shoutout to Nintendo, THQ and H2O for making this great game.

Note: Not sure what happened at around the 29th minute but it seems my audio cut out for a few seconds. Sorry about that.
